# Path-based publish governance for kryos-registry.
#
# At launch, NORTHTEKDevs maintainers own everything. As packages mature
# and gain stable authors, ownership lines for specific package paths
# can be added below so that subsequent versions can be auto-approved
# by the package's established author(s).
#
# Format:
#   <prefix>/<name>.json @github_username[, @another_username]
#
# The catch-all keeps everything maintainer-reviewed until per-package
# overrides land.

*       @NORTHTEKDevs/maintainers
